<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background-color:#f4f4f5;">
<table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color:#f4f4f5;">
  <tr>
    <td align="center" style="padding:40px 16px;">
      <table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="max-width:560px;width:100%;">
        <tr>
          <td style="background-color:#ffffff;border:1px solid #e4e4e7;border-radius:10px;padding:36px 40px;font-family:-apple-system,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;color:#27272a;">
            <p style="margin:0 0 4px;font-size:13px;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#71717a;">{{.Hostname}}</p>
            <h1 style="margin:0 0 16px;font-size:24px;font-weight:600;color:#18181b;">Welcome!</h1>
            <p style="margin:0 0 24px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;">
              Your mail server is up and running.
            </p>
            <table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="width:100%;margin:0 0 24px;">
              <tr>
                <td style="padding:10px 0;border-top:1px solid #f4f4f5;font-size:14px;color:#71717a;width:120px;">Admin panel</td>
                <td style="padding:10px 0;border-top:1px solid #f4f4f5;font-size:14px;"><a href="{{.AdminURL}}" style="color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">{{.AdminURL}}</a></td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td style="padding:10px 0;border-top:1px solid #f4f4f5;font-size:14px;color:#71717a;">Webmail</td>
                <td style="padding:10px 0;border-top:1px solid #f4f4f5;font-size:14px;"><a href="{{.WebmailURL}}" style="color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">{{.WebmailURL}}</a></td>
              </tr>
            </table>
            <p style="margin:0{{if .Key}} 0 28px{{end}};font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;color:#52525b;">
              Mail apps on your phone or computer can usually configure
              themselves; just enter your address and password.
            </p>
{{if .Key}}
            <h2 style="margin:0 0 8px;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#18181b;">Your backup recovery key</h2>
            <p style="margin:0 0 14px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;color:#52525b;">
              Backups of this server are encrypted. Restoring them after a
              disaster requires the secret key below; without it, backups
              are unreadable.
            </p>
            <div style="font-family:ui-monospace,'SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;background-color:#f4f4f5;border:1px solid #e4e4e7;border-radius:6px;padding:14px 16px;word-break:break-all;color:#18181b;">{{.Key}}</div>
            <p style="margin:14px 0 0;font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;color:#71717a;">
              Keep a copy somewhere that is not this server: a password
              manager is ideal. Keeping this email in a mail app on another
              device also works. One caution: if you forward your mail to
              another provider, this key travels with it.
            </p>
{{end}}
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding:20px 8px 0;text-align:center;font-family:-apple-system,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#a1a1aa;">
            Sent once by {{.Hostname}} when it was first set up.
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>
</body>
</html>
